buttonLinkCriticalBackground.comment: Used for the background of critical ButtonLink in the default state.

buttonLinkCriticalBackgroundActive.comment: Used for the background of critical ButtonLink in the active and the focus state.

formElementBorderColorFocus.comment: Should be used for all form-elements when the component has active or focus state and it's needed to render border attribute, or combined with shadows.

formElementBorderColorError.comment: Should be used for all form-elements when the component has error state and it's needed to render border attribute, or combined with shadows.

foundation.name: formElementFocusBoxShadow
foundation.value: inset 0 0 0 1px color(#0172CB, opacity: 100), inset 0 0 0 3px color(#0172CB, opacity: 15)

foundation.name: formElementErrorFocusBoxShadow
foundation.value: inset 0 0 0 1px color(#D21C1C, opacity: 100), inset 0 0 0 3px color(#D21C1C, opacity: 15)

formElementForeground.comment: Should be used for the text when they value is not filled.
